high_descs: Turn left and head to the fridge on the right.
Pick up the spatula from the fridge.
Head to the diningtable on the left and turn around.
Put the spatula on the diningtable.
Walk to the microwave on the right.
Pick up the spatula from the microwave.
Head right to face the right side of the diningtable.
Put the spatula on the diningtable with the other spatula.
anns.task_desc: Put two Spatulas on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn towards your left and take few steps and again turn your right side and walk towards the fridge.
Open the fridge and take the spatula from it and close the door.
turn left and walk towards the diningtable in which oven is placed.
Put the spatula on the side of the diningtable.
Then come to the front of the microwave and stand in front of the oven.
Open the oven and take the spatula out of the oven and close the door.
Turn right and move towards the corner of the diningtable.
Put the spatula on the side of the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Keep the Spatula on the side of the DiningTable

high_descs: walk to the fridge and go to the cabinet.
open the cabinet and take out the spatula from in it.
turn around and walk over to the diningtable.
stop and look at the diningtable.
walk to the table that has on it the microwave.
Open the door to the microwave with the spatula and then close it.
walk back to the diningtable.
Put down the spatula on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Get all the spatula and put them on the dining table.
